NotificationCatcher - Class in com.forst.lukas.pibe.service
This class provide service that listens to the notifications and then send them via broadcast to the other classes.
Sending to the computer via LAN can be turned off / on by modifying boolean canSendNotification.

There's bug present in the Android since version 4.4.

Receiver used for receiving commands from all over the application - typically request for active notifications.
